p: In the District Court for the Third Judicial District of Washington Terriotry holding terms at Seattle in King County within and for the counties of King, Kitsap and Snohomish
The President of the United States of America to Lewis V Wyckoff Sheriff of King County Greeting

We command you that you have the body of Peter Nelson W Smith H Elsner C Whaley G Mattson Charls Lundblud Dennis Coffy and Jacob Anner by you imprisoned and detained as it is said.. together with the time and cause of such imprisonment and detention. before the Hon J.R. Lewis Chief Justice of Washington Territory and Judge of the District Court aforesaid at the Chambers of said Judge in the City of Seattle county and Territory aforesaid on the 3d day of May AD 1875. at the hour of one OClock PM of said day to do and receive what shall then and there be considered concerning therein and have you then
and there this writ
Witness the Hon J.R. Lewis Chief Justice of Washington Territory and Judge of said District Court this 1st day of May AD 1875
Attest my hand and the seal of said court affixed the day and date last above written
